United in Fight against prOstate cancer (UFO) registry: first results from a 
large, multi-centre, prospective, longitudinal cohort study of advanced prostate 
cancer in Asia.

Uemura H(1), Ye D(2), Kanesvaran R(3), Chiong E(4), Lojanapiwat B(5), Pu YS(6), 
Rawal SK(7), Abdul Razack AH(8), Zeng H(9), Chung BH(10), Md Yusoff NA(11), 
Ohyama C(12), Kim CS(13), Leewansangtong S(14), Tsai YS(15), Liu Y(16), Liu 
